## â“ FAQ

### Common Questions

**Q: Why pnpm instead of npm or yarn?**
A: pnpm offers faster installs, better disk space efficiency, and stricter dependency resolution.

**Q: Can I use React instead of Svelte?**
A: Yes! Astro supports multiple frameworks. Install `@astrojs/react` and swap component files.

**Q: How do I add new pages?**
A: Create `.astro` files in `src/pages/`. File-based routing is automatic.

**Q: Is this production-ready?**
A: Yes! This boilerplate includes all necessary production optimizations and security measures.

